        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>11:15</td>
          <td>Demo Session          <br/>
          <div style="margin-left:18px">
            Champion: <a
            href="http://ontolog.cim3.net/cgi-bin/wiki.pl?MarkUnderwood">Mark Underwood</a>
